\begin_inset Formula $z\left(t\right)$
\end_inset

 converges to 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{U}$
\end_inset

.
 Furthermore, since 
\begin_inset Formula $z\left(t\right)\in\mathcal{D}$
\end_inset

 for all 
