\end_inset

 holds for all time.
\begin_inset Note Note
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Consider 
\begin_inset Formula $z\in\mathcal{B}\subset\mathbb{R}^{\varphi}.$
\end_inset

 Then
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\Vert z\right\Vert \leq R_{\mathcal{B}}
\]

